trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException" /> class exception is thrown when an Active Directory Domain Services object is created and that object already exists in the underlying directory store.
trans-unit.target: 當建立 Active Directory 網域服務物件，且該物件已經存在於基礎目錄存放區中時，會擲回<see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryObjectExistsException" /> 類別例外狀況。
